name: "peace" Whitney Houston Anniversary T-Shirt Pre-Order
description: This year marks the 2 year anniversary of the passing of our beloved Whitney E. Houston. Every year I make a new shirt to wear for that year and on that day. As usual, other Nippy Lovers want to know where I get my one of a kind shirts and how they too can get one just like it. SOOOOOO, The Nippy Shop (my old shop my friend Madi and I had for Nippy) decided to make this shirt available for purchase. This is the Pre-Order going until Thursday 12/19/13. After all those are sold out, we will be releasing only the limited amount we have left of the "peace" Whitney Houston Anniversary Shirts. ALL SHIRTS WILL BE DELIVERED TO YOU BY 02/11/14.

name: Kindred Hearts Petit cupCates BowTie
description:
The Kindred Hearts Petit cupCates BowTie was inspired by the Nicole cupCates BowTie that was created for Breast Cancer Month. It was adored and loved by many, so I decided to make an entire collection of different colors. This bowtie was created because of the love I have for my family, because of our connection, because they are my world, my hearts. So in Honor of my cousin Nicole who passed away from Breast Cancer in August, in honor of my family who are indeed some survivors, in honor of our love and our willingness to be there for one another, I dedicated this bowtie to them to my family. Please enjoy the Kindred Hearts Petit cupCates BowTie 

It's chic, it's stylish. It's unique. It's beautiful. There are 8 colors to choose from. 
Width: 5.5 cm
Length: 10 cm
The center strip is made by faux leather. 
 
Colors Available:
Red 
Black
Orange is the New Black
Champagne
Navy Blue
Winter White
Seven Shades of Grey
violet purple

You don't want to not have one of these amazing BowTies $17 plus shipping!
